# vhs tape — records docs/demo.gif (the 15-second launch asset, SPEC §6)
# Regenerate: vhs docs/demo.tape  (needs `housebroken` on PATH; content is the
# bundled synthetic demo — never record real history into this GIF)

Output docs/demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 15
Set Width 1220
Set Height 780
Set Padding 16
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 55ms

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Show

Sleep 600ms
Type "housebroken demo"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1.2s
Sleep 9s
